article.headline: Cleary scores 23, Le Moyne downs Fairleigh Dickinson 74-63
article.description: — Kaiyem Cleary had 23 points in Le Moyne's 74-63 victory over Fairleigh Dickinson on Saturday.
article.linkText: Cleary scores 23, Le Moyne downs Fairleigh Dickinson 74-63
article.story: TEANECK, N.J. -- — Kaiyem Cleary had 23 points in Le Moyne's 74-63 victory over Fairleigh Dickinson on Saturday. Cleary had eight rebounds for the Dolphins (6-9, 1-0 Northeast Conference). AJ Dancier shot 3 for 4, including 2 for 3 from beyond the arc to add 10 points. Trent Mosquera was 4 of 10 shooting (2 for 5 from 3-point range) to finish with 10 points. Sean Moore led the way for the Knights (6-10, 0-2) with 20 points and 12 rebounds. Terrence Brown added nine points for Fairleigh Dickinson. In addition, DeVante Jamison finished with eight points and three steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
